00:25:24.330 --> 00:25:27.830
moving from one part
of Pashtun territory

00:25:27.830 --> 00:25:30.480
to another part of
Pashtun territory,

00:25:30.480 --> 00:25:34.200
which is separated by a line--
that the British imposed--

00:25:34.200 --> 00:25:37.560
the Durand line-- which the
Afghans have never accepted

00:25:37.560 --> 00:25:40.210
and the Pashtun
have never accepted.

00:25:40.210 --> 00:25:43.210
Now that happens everywhere.

