President Obama, one
of his achievements

00:25:45.430 --> 00:25:49.380
has been to break all
records in deporting

00:25:49.380 --> 00:25:54.120
undocumented immigrants--
almost two million.

00:25:54.120 --> 00:25:59.220
They're crossing a border--
the Mexico US border--

00:25:59.220 --> 00:26:02.710
which, like state
borders generally,

00:26:02.710 --> 00:26:06.330
was established by brutal
violence and aggression.

