The same kind of people
living on both sides

00:26:22.540 --> 00:26:24.410
until pretty recently.

00:26:24.410 --> 00:26:27.600
It's been heavily
militarized now.

00:26:27.600 --> 00:26:29.980
Primarily since NAFTA.

