00:26:55.210 --> 00:26:56.167
Agro-business.

00:26:56.167 --> 00:26:58.000
So there's going to be
a flow of immigrants.

00:26:58.000 --> 00:27:01.210
So we've got to militarize
the border to prevent them.

00:27:01.210 --> 00:27:02.630
Send them back.

